<emphasis box="[291,390,297,320]" italics="true" pageId="8" pageNumber="9">L. curtus</emphasis>
(
<bibRefCitation author="Gritis" box="[405,636,295,319]" pageId="8" pageNumber="9" refString="Gritis, P. A. &amp; Voris, H. K. (1990) Variability and significance of parietal and ventral scales in the marine snakes of the genus Lapemis (Serpentes: Hydrophiidae), with comments on the occurrence of spiny scales in the genus. Fieldiana Zoology, 56, 1 - 13." type="journal article" year="1990">
